title: Tech set to defend home turf against No. 21 NC State - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech set to defend home turf against No. 21 NC State  VT hokiesports.com
description: Having won eight of its last nine games, the Virginia Tech baseball team (18-7, 5-5 ACC) will set out to claim its fourth consecutive ACC series this weekend when it welcomes No. 21 NC State (18-9, 6-5 ACC) to English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park for a three-game series (April 8-10).
